{"tid":1974550,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"砌機後開唔著，一長兩短一長三短都出現晒","createTime":"2020-04-16T02:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T04:12:06.000Z","uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dafa8e4651a8f3374676dfba2c89635ae862cbc7","tid":1974550,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"List<br />\n<br />\nCpu: amd 3600<br />\nMB: Asus B450m-plus gaming<br />\nRam: thermaltake toughram 2x8GB DDR4 3600MHZ C18<br />\n火牛：fsp raider 2 650w 80plus sliver<br />\n<br />\n上述新野<br />\n<br />\n下面係舊料<br />\n<br />\nGpu: rx570<br />\nSsd: 860evo<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n裸跑上陣，砌機時已確保4+4pin隊落cpu，20+4pin隊落最長個位，Hdmi肯定插住gpu<br />\n<br />\n神奇嘅事嚟啦，第一次開機，bios認到晒，揀save and exit。<br />\n<br />\n裝埋入箱，再開機，無畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎出嚟裸跑，除晒front io線同其他林林總總嘅線。bios speaker 一長兩短，cpu fan / ram rgb / mb rgb 有燈但無畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再嚟，cut電源拔火牛線，reset cmos（拔電芯等成晚+用一字批隊落mb個兩枝針+起身裝番），今次一長三短，cpu fan / ram rgb / mb rgb / mouse keyboard 全部有燈，都係無畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已拎擦膠擦gpu 金手指，上面每步都有熄火牛拔埋條三腳線先落手，入箱過程無再郁過cpu，金三角形肯定有對住底板灰三角形。<br />\n<br />\n請問各位高手點處理好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gszA8Qr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgszA8Qr.png&h=efce27cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJxi6wR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJxi6wR.png&h=487c5d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0mTaYJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0mTaYJ.png&h=7e2986dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igTeESf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigTeESf.png&h=421e53cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2d46efa6d2b959934a135b46ee9fcce1369d178","tid":1974550,"uid":215558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"9f607c761094476f12e1c3740453adedfc317994","tid":1974550,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2d46efa6d2b959934a135b46ee9fcce1369d178","tid":1974550,"uid":215558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thanks<br />\n<br />\n尋晚六點砌撚到八點諗住終於有番電腦用<br />\n<br />\n頂佢個肺搞到依加都仲未用到 頭都爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係留住張顯示卡，一早拎俾人砌算鳩數"},{"pid":"7435e159d97afac650337966524e615a4bfbdf34","tid":1974550,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"插底板display得唔得"},{"pid":"214b86da8655d795cb4c3828925938041b2cac39","tid":1974550,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c13de530e8890798bf564908626cd5049fb8327","tid":1974550,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"重裝系統"},{"pid":"d39afe7098cf7e1ada2da238f801e77ac6339911","tid":1974550,"uid":137096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"瘋狂抽插下啲ram+換位+1條開機試下"},{"pid":"29984a46cdd509b6d71a493bf804ee8e5fe09ccc","tid":1974550,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"video card 問題，你入 bios 睇吓，有冇 set 好，試吓用 onboard 睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hk